<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٦ في <span class="c1">"ق"</span> <span class="c1">"عمله"</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>